 What in heaven is Flat Beat ?What is Flat Eric ?Who is MR OIZO ?  (ojzoo ??)A few weeks ago, I asked the same question to my kids, when we were watching Ultratop a Belgian Hitparade-program on our national broadcasting company. (on Ketnet, presented by Heidi d’Heer)My childeren 7 years and 9 years, tried to explain it to me, but then I saw the clip, with the funnie yellow cat, dog, bear or whatever on his desk, signing papers, making telephonecalls and typing on a keyboard,and... I liked it.And I was not the only one, because it was a number one hit for several weeks.The character allready has appeared in a Levis-commercial, for their sta-pressed jeans, where he is heavy shaking sitting in a car.It was created by Quentin Dupieux.The French House hit again, (after Daft Punks’ “around the world”)So I surfed the net, bought the record, and made this IconsetIt’s not finished yet, every time when I find new images, I will make an update.The pronounciation of Mr Oizo is“oiseau”, as in french (bird)Thanx to Quentin Dupieux (the creator of the caracter, and music)the “stupid 55” studiographisists Laetitea Caillie & HotspotMr Oizo tag by RockDO NOT EAT THIS RECORD Have fun Peter Coen (kewlox)BelgiumPeter.Coen@ping.be